{
  "id": "adv_event_2502_01_05_02",
  "title": "あなたに\nハッピー\nバレンタイン",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――バレンタインイベント終了後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—After the Valentine’s event",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.5246609047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "みんなお疲れ様。バレンタインらしい愛に溢れた\n素敵なステージだったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Great work‚ everyone. It was a stage overflowing\nwith Valentine’s-style love—truly wonderful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.3579937294,
      "endTime": 7.9333340002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.1750462209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！\n私達もお客さんの声援から沢山の愛をもらいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much!\nWe received so much love from the audience’s cheers as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.1750462209,
      "endTime": 15.2766771947,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.4833436324
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "ファンも、私達も、みんな幸せ……\nバレンタインイベント、やって良かった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The fans‚ us… everyone is happy…\nI’m glad we did this Valentine’s event…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.4833436324,
      "endTime": 23.202617962399998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（みんなが誰に本命チョコを渡したのか気になるが……）\n（今の幸せそうな彼女達に、水を差すなんて出来ないな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I’m curious about who everyone gave their true feeling Valentine chocolate to‚ but…）\n（I can’t spoil their happiness right now.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.395951334,
      "endTime": 32.9906452808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.1773117376
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（余計な詮索はやめておこう。みんなが幸せなら、俺は）\n（どんな相手だろうと受け入れ……受け入れ……ぐぬぬ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I should stop prying. As long as they’re happy‚）\n（I’ll accept it no matter who it is… accept it… ngh…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.1773117376,
      "endTime": 45.6744772268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ところで、{user}君。今夜チョコを\n寮に持って来る約束ちゃんと覚えてるわよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ {user}. You remember your promise\nto bring the chocolates to the dorm tonight‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.8611436837,
      "endTime": 52.2505539887,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.4505540841
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "大事な話があるので、忘れずに来て下さいね\n待ってますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have something important to talk about‚\nso please don’t forget. We’ll be waiting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.4505540841,
      "endTime": 57.6666655534,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.9381372604
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（大事な話？　まさか、みんなの好きな人を……）\n（恋人を俺に打ち明けるつもりなのか！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Something important? Don’t tell me…）\n（Are they about to tell me who they love… their partners!?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.9381372604,
      "endTime": 67.5874796066,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.800812959
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（私生活には口出ししないようにしていたが）\n（サニピ全員に恋人がいたなんて……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I’ve avoided interfering in their private lives‚ but…）\n（If every Sunny Peace member has a partner…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.800812959,
      "endTime": 74.42172007490001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.6283867035
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（一体いつからこんなことに……）\n（これが世間に知られたら大変なことになるぞ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Since when did this happen…）\n（If the public finds out‚ it’ll be a disaster!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.6283867035,
      "endTime": 81.231629387,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.4382960154
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん？\nどうかしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san?\nIs something wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.4382960154,
      "endTime": 84.99999888670001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "あ……いや、なんでもない……\n俺なら大丈夫だ。しっかり寮までチョコを届けるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… no‚ it’s nothing…\nI’m fine. I’ll make sure to bring the chocolates to the dorm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.263715362,
      "endTime": 92.827887916,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.0145547544
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（落ち着け、みんなは俺を信頼して話すつもりなんだ）\n（だったら俺も、みんなの信頼に応えないと！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Calm down. They’re planning to talk because they trust me.）\n（Then I need to live up to that trust!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.0145547544,
      "endTime": 103.055574957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.2422416999
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "……しっかり俺も心の準備をして行くよ\nみんながどんな決断をしようとちゃんと受け止めるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’ll prepare myself mentally before I go.\nNo matter what decisions you’ve made‚ I’ll accept them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.2422416999,
      "endTime": 114.3922420814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.1333322201
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.6055754339
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "だから信じてほしい……\n何があっても、俺はみんなの味方だ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So please trust me…\nNo matter what happens‚ I’m on your side!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.6055754339,
      "endTime": 121.0026504194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その日の夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Later that night",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.0159836764,
      "endTime": 123.2065938629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "事務所に届いていたチョコを全部持って来たから\n自分の分は部屋に運んでおいてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I brought all the chocolates that arrived at the office‚\nso take your own portions to your rooms.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.1159862196,
      "endTime": 130.1623579657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "……それで、俺に大事な話があるんだよな？\n覚悟は出来ている。みんなの話を聞かせてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So‚ you had something important to tell me‚ right?\nI’m ready. Let me hear what you have to say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.3756911273,
      "endTime": 139.43467092470001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました、勇気を出して打ち明けますね\n{user}さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright. I’ll gather my courage and tell you.\n{user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.62800401,
      "endTime": 149.2445088067,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12838.662656699995
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "いつもありがとうございます！\nこれ、私達の気持ちです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for everything‚ always!\nThis is how we feel!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.5264331176,
      "endTime": 154.5325455024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "こ、これは、もしかして……\n……バレンタインのチョコレート？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-this is… could it be…\n…Valentine’s chocolate?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.8258848344,
      "endTime": 162.2957943115,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　みんなで手作りしたんですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! We all made it together by hand!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.5024610354,
      "endTime": 165.8301934077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "鳩が豆鉄砲を食らったような顔をしてるわね\nそんなに意外だったかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You look like a pigeon that just got hit with a pea shooter.\nWas it really that surprising?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.0435267602,
      "endTime": 172.49520484549998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "サプライズ大成功……ぶい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Surprise was a huge success… V!",
        "id": ""
      },
