    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "手作りのチョコを俺に？　そうだったのか……\n自分がもらうなんて全然考えてなかったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Handmade chocolate… for me? So that’s what it was…\nI never once thought I’d be the one receiving it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.0981424246,
      "endTime": 187.5384603415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "いつもお世話になってるんだから当然です。むしろ\nどうして私達からもらえないと思ったのか聞きたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re always taking care of us‚ so of course. If anything‚\nI want to know why you thought you wouldn’t get anything from us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.7384604369,
      "endTime": 195.6906601822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "……もしかして、迷惑でしたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Was it a bother?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.9039932484,
      "endTime": 199.2511808152,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこと、ある訳ないだろ。凄く嬉しいよ\nみんな、ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no way. I’m incredibly happy.\nThank you‚ everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.4511809106,
      "endTime": 208.1166460747,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうを言うのは……\n感謝を伝えるのは私達の方です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The ones who should be saying thank you…\nthe ones who should be sharing gratitude are us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.3233127987,
      "endTime": 214.1500247395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "大変なことも沢山あったけど\nずっとマネージャーで居続けてくれてありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There were so many hard times‚ but\nthank you for staying our manager all this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.3433579679,
      "endTime": 220.3573944325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "私達を見つけてくれて……\nアイドルにしてくれて、ありがとう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for finding us…\nand for making us idols…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.5573943372,
      "endTime": 226.485440373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "いつもそばにいて、見守ってくれて\nありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for always being by our side\nand watching over us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 226.6854405637,
      "endTime": 231.63329153,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "私達の居場所を……\nサニーピースを作ってくれて、ありがとうございます",
